nodes.text: Senator Wren's Social Calendar is an article written by Morrie Mullins as a tie in to the Living Force campaign adventure An Official Engagement. It was published on the Wizards of the Coast website on January 24 2002 as the first of the Year Two articles. It took the form of an in-universe report by Yara Grugara on the activities of Senator Lavina Wren with particular focus on an unknown love interest in her life.
